Key Project Requirements
Project Title: SCHOLARITY 
What is our project?
Our prototype is a software that helps students, it asks you what program you take, it can be anything IGCSE, ALEVELS, OLEVELS, AUSMATH and many more, it helps you get access to resources, educational resources like, past papers, notes, references, books, slides, question bank, videos, lectures, tutors, teachers etc, the main goal is to align students with the academic success  
The Goal: Develop a prototype for a software solution targeting one of specific SDGs: Education, 
The Tools: You must use Trello for Agile management and GitHub for version control and documentation.

The Warning: If you use AI to generate any part of the report, diagrams, or code, that section will receive zero marks. Use me only for "inspiration or general research".
